snippet.textDisplay: I know this is very general, but this really brings back memories of when i used to go to the arcades with my dad when i was a kid. We would play all these games together and at the end we would trade all the tickets for dumb prizes. Air hockey was and still is my favourite one to this day, i really have a soft spot for that game because of those good moments. Seeing the grumps play all these games and with their kind of humour makes me really nostalgic and happy.
